Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.85,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ma quanti cavolo sono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.12,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Non posso certo ignorarli!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.46,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ma non ho tempo per salvarli tutti!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:43.40,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Merda, cosa faccio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:47.02,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,La stazione e il prof Gojo sono poco più avanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.14,Main,Inumaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uova di merluzzo marinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.36,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Quel modo di esprimersi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.16,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai Inumaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:52.94,Main,Inumaki,0000,0000,0000,,Salmone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.77,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Te li affido!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.00,Main,Inumaki,0000,0000,0000,,Salmone, salmone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.43,Main,Inumaki,0000,0000,0000,,Non muovetevi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.96,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episodio 37\N{\fs30\fscy150}Fosforo Rosso
